text: Chansopheak (born 15 June 1999) is a Cambodian footballer who plays for Visakha in the Cambodian League and the Cambodia U-23. ==Club career== Ken Chansopheak made his senior debut in Cambodia League in 2019 For Visakha. ==International career== Ken Chansopheak made his junior international debut in 2020 AFC U-23 Championship qualification against Australia national under-23 soccer team on 22 March 2019. ==External links== * Ken Chansopheak at NationalFootballTeams Category:Living people Category:Cambodia international footballers Category:1999 births Category:People from Takéo Province Category:Cambodian footballers Category:Association football defenders
